  <span id="freeText2531140034337789569" style="display:none">A fantastic experience that's clearly a dream yet the story is reminiscent of everything we all have to deal with in the real world every day.<br /><br />A dream that's clearly the real world yet the story is too lovely to be real, and too painful not to be.<br /><br />Dreams that are dreams within dreams that may hold meaning but it's hidden from me.<br /><br />Read it. You may regret it. But you won't forget it.</span>
